race.description: Brett Bowman Racing & Breeding Super Mdn Hcp
race.comment: FRATIANNO (2) two runs back have had merit and caught the eye again when a slashing third over 1100m at Coonamble. Apprentice Nick Palmer retains the ride and he's looking for the 1200m now. Among the top chances. UNSOLVED (1) kept safe in betting at his first run back when a wilting sixth over 1100m at Coonamble. Gets a more economical run and senior rider takes the reins. Likely improver. HINTO (8) huge run from the awkward gate second up when a gritty sixth over 1200m at Tamworth. Poorly drawn again but best figures are good enough to play a leading role. BULLANT (6) improving filly who looks close to shedding her maiden status. Speared across from the wide barrier when a fighting second over 1100m at Coonamble first-up. No shock to see her take this out.
